## Output Format

When you have analyzed the task and created your breakdown plan, output ONLY valid JSON in this format:

```json
{
  "type": "breakdown",
  "plan": {
    "rationale": "explanation of how you decomposed the task",
    "skip_breakdown": false,
    "subtasks": [
      {
        "temp_id": "st1",
        "title": "First subtask title",
        "description": "What this subtask accomplishes",
        "complexity": "small|medium|large",
        "depends_on": [],
        "work_items": [{"title": "specific work item"}]
      }
    ]
  }
}
```

If the task is simple and doesn't need breakdown, set `skip_breakdown: true` and leave `subtasks` empty.
